name: 迈克尔·戴尔
introduction: Mike Dell is an actor and a professional wrestler. He has been acting since 2012 and has been a professional wrestler since 1999. He started training to be a wrestler while living in New Jersey till moving to Texas in 2001 and continued his career in the wrestling world to this day. The acting bug bit him in early 2012 when he decided to see an acting coach. Now, with his time split between acting and wrestling, he has been busy in the commercial and TV/film world.
